    ?亙??脖????鈭斗?銵剁?瘝?? equity/cash嚗?????閰衣?鈭斗???遣??
    
    Args:
        trades_or_ds: 瘥??????DataFrame ??漱??” DataFrame
        df_raw: ?寞??豢? DataFrame嚗???潮?撱箸????蝺??
    
    Returns:
        go.Figure: Plotly ??”?拐辣
    """
